{%- comment -%}
  IWANT / InSales / Liquid integration for chat-me.

  How to use:
  1. Replace the old Telegram block with this snippet.
  2. Set the real storefront host in chat-me `allowed_origins` for `insales-store`.
  3. If your privacy policy page has a custom URL, replace `PRIVACY_URL` below.
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="contact-float-group{% if template == 'product' %} product-page-btns{% endif %}">
  <a
    href="#shop-chat"
    rel="nofollow noopener"
    class="contact-fix-btn"
    data-chat-me-trigger
    aria-label="Открыть чат с магазином"
  >
    Чат
  </a>
</div>

